HEADWORD: Soldanrie
<hw>Sol"dan*rie</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The country ruled
by a soldan, or sultan; a sultanate{2}.</def> <mark>[Poet.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
